name: AlimikAR
tagline: iOs advertising Application developed for Alimik (Bologna, Italy).
body:
# AlimikAR
Alimik AR is a simple iOs Augmented Reality application developed using the Metaio Framework.
Its main purpose is to test the possibilities offered by MetaioSDK and iOs SDK to realize advertising applications.
